Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:00:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,書店和我們的營業部強烈要求
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在發售日舉辦簽名會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,地點是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,簽名會之類的簡直荒謬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.36,0:01:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,無法控制的東西就要徹底避開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.91,0:01:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道朏君會這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.03,0:01:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,很遺憾 我去轉告營業部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不開門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,反正是推銷的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.48,0:01:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我去好好拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可是有時會有無法控制的人們…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 素晴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是大翔君哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:01:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,會奇襲過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:37.48,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1006.222,556)\fad(350,350)\blur3}控制不住的你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你們來跟素晴哥哥打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我是矢坂隼翔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小學三年級
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我是矢坂鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,也是小學三年級
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,隼翔和鳴海如你所見 是雙胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我是海空 3歲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真了不起呢 能好好介紹自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚媽媽她們突然有事要出門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我就早退回家照顧他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,跟小孩子們說了陽的事情後他們就非要來看了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你來我已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 你見到他們還是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,渚你見過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說你是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見 今天突然來這麼多人很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大概在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好 找出小陽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想快點見到牠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也一起去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,河瀨先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,發現小陽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不能這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,河瀨先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,想跟小陽一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想去玩想去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真想去啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,重新泡杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,素晴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一如既往什麼都沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,別隨意翻人家冰箱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:05:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦 這是定期檢查哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你有沒有好好吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天 大概吃過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,首先每天都要吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,外賣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:15.85,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\an2\fsp2.5\blur1\fnFZYaSong-R-GBK\fs25\frz43.42\pos(100.122,465.091)}中華料理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:15.85,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur1\an2\fsp9\fnFZYaSong-R-GBK\fs25\frz43.42\pos(170.182,550.909)}春來軒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:15.85,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur1\an2\fnFZYaSong-R-GBK\fs20\frz43.42\pos(270.546,662.909)}外賣菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,晚餐點這裡的外賣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是我請客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,輕點 海空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,下一個我想抱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,來 轉到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,今天在素晴哥哥家點外送哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,河瀨先生可以的話也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我要天經飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:49.63,Comment,,0,0,0,,註: 誤讀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,天津飯嗎 不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我要拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我去做一下餐前準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:06:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不懂該怎麼跟小孩子接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而且這麼多小孩來我家是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 有那麼多人的杯子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼我可以幫忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,去便利商店買紙杯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 素晴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,旅遊時看到了茶杯套裝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,太漂亮了就買了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多客人來的時候用 不覺得很棒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有那種時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 肯定會有的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:08:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,到那時候大家一起用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你家裡書真不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,1 2 3 4
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…我在學校是圖書委員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,現在是讀書周 我正在做推薦書列表
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不對 小朋友應該喝麥茶更好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,素晴先生有推薦的書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,推薦的書?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這本有貓出場 我很推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到這次輪到我被問到這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,說到底 喜歡的書首先就不可能濃縮到一本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 內容的優秀也不是一句話就能說清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而且年齡和性別都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,能否興趣相投還不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,推薦是什麼 該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:15.86,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an2\bord1.5\fn@FZYaSong-B-GBK\fax-0.3\pos(598.222,399.556)\frz270\3c&H1A2B8F&\4c&H1A2B8F&\shad2.5}焙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:15.86,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs30\fn@FZKai-Z03\b1\fsp3\fax-0.3\frz270\c&H163195&\bord0\pos(485.169,337.723)}袋泡茶　
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:15.86,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs25\c&H163195&\bord0\fn@FZYaSong-M-GBK\fax-0.3\fay-0.03\frz270\pos(418.2,310.9)}100%國產茶葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:15.86,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs25\c&H163195&\fay0.3\fnFZYaSong-H-GBK\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(663.111,522.222)}實惠裝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:15.86,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs20\fscy120\c&H000000&\fnFZYaSong-R-GBK\fay0.3\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(695.111,598.222)}60包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是我套交情太唐突了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你一樣大的時候 曾經沉醉於這本書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可以借給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 什麼時候還都行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣推薦就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待讀這本書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,春來軒外賣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,開動!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,天經飯真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是天津飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,拉麵看起來也好香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真的欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微嚐嚐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,海空也要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,終於結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就能安靜地…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要玩捉迷藏的人都過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,躲好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,躲好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,躲好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好 在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪裡在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起做鬼臉　嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,認輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,素晴君鬼臉遊戲好強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,素晴君 過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽超可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真少見啊 是來客人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真熱鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,隼翔 鳴海 該回家了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,小海空睡著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,還想最後再抱一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,已經玩夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,素晴 今天多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真開心啊 素晴君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧 素晴君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再給你帶我媽媽做的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 已經混得相當熟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再玩啊 素晴君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,下次我帶班上的朋友來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,朏君 那就明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,鳴海明天也要來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,行了行了 素晴哥哥會為難的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,做了不習慣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,呼嚕?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,無法控制的東西必須避開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不擅長應付意外的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 在意外之後 才能遇見小小的發現與邂逅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 偶爾…真的只是非常偶爾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可能也不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微考慮一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:19.58,Cat,,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:22.64,Cat,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:26.24,Cat,,0,0,0,,敵人來襲嗎 這裡應該很安靜才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:33.56,Cat,,0,0,0,,對了 虎姐說過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.16,Cat,,0,0,0,,不論何時都不能鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.72,Cat,,0,0,0,,隨時做好戰鬥的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.94,Cat,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我不能逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.36,Cat,,0,0,0,,放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 隼翔 鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,大吵大鬧窮追不捨是不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.21,Cat,,0,0,0,,那個人類是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:56.19,Cat,,0,0,0,,這些傢伙是他的爪牙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:59.75,Cat,,0,0,0,,這可不能鬆懈了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,它和海空一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真的欸 好可愛的蝴蝶結
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,小貓快過來快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:08.82,Cat,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.62,Cat,,0,0,0,,但又不能逃走…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:13.15,Cat,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:15.03,Cat,,0,0,0,,他走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.39,Cat,,0,0,0,,現在還剩下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:20.51,Cat,,0,0,0,,這幾個看起來很弱的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.61,Cat,,0,0,0,,他被我的氣場嚇跑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}小陽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:27.79,Cat,,0,0,0,,這傢伙出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.15,Cat,,0,0,0,,現在又輪到他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:31.37,Cat,,0,0,0,,這些人一個接一個搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:35.88,Cat,,0,0,0,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:39.07,Cat,,0,0,0,,糟了 被繞到背後了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.63,Cat,,0,0,0,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:53.11,Cat,,0,0,0,,人類的幼崽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:57.29,Cat,,0,0,0,,你要保護他們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:00.44,Cat,,0,0,0,,小孩子是很弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為小陽要抓你了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真老實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:14.58,Cat,,0,0,0,,欺負弱小有違我的原則
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看來小陽也不討厭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想抱抱 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多該放開她了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:29.44,Cat,,0,0,0,,雖然他們很煩不過反正看起來也不是我的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:35.48,Cat,,0,0,0,,已經好了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:40.98,Cat,,0,0,0,,所以他們到底是要幹什麼啊 真是不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:43.98,Cat,,0,0,0,,總算能鬆口氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,春來軒外賣!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:55.13,Cat,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:56.65,Cat,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:18:00.03,Cat,,0,0,0,,這個味道是!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是你朋友的家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:13.83,Cat,,0,0,0,,這是超級美味的飯的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不是的 我們是來哥哥的朋友家裡玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:17.87,Cat,,0,0,0,,啊這誘人的芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 這是之前的那隻貓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是那個小貪吃鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她原來住在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,小春 你認識小陽?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}給你錢 金額正好呢 謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你們的名字讀起來一樣欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 以前她經常來我們家吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是突然就不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看到她這麼有精神我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,原來我們的名字一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,額 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 春(陽)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:50.21,Cat,,0,0,0,,什麼!吃飯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:52.49,Cat,,0,0,0,,我現在就想吃 想吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜 下次再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.98,Cat,,0,0,0,,這些食物是給我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:03.52,Cat,,0,0,0,,快拿來快拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}躲好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.78,Cat,,0,0,0,,等等 你們要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:10.69,Cat,,0,0,0,,我想去那邊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:23.00,Cat,,0,0,0,,這張臉還真是充滿挑釁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小陽你贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:29.63,Cat,,0,0,0,,欸?有什麼好笑的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我帶了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:38.17,Cat,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:40.12,Cat,,0,0,0,,那裡好像有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:47.33,Cat,,0,0,0,,它跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:55.46,Cat,,0,0,0,,這是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:57.50,Cat,,0,0,0,,我的身體停不下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 加我一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,下次我帶班上的朋友來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:30.26,Cat,,0,0,0,,他們總算…回去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:35.17,Cat,,0,0,0,,那孩子也倒下了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:38.27,Cat,,0,0,0,,嗯 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:41.01,Cat,,0,0,0,,你振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:46.17,Cat,,0,0,0,,我可告訴你 我比你辛苦多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:52.33,Cat,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:57.64,Cat,,0,0,0,,這個味道很溫暖又讓人安心…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.55,Cat,,0,0,0,,無論何時你都不能放鬆警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:04.21,Cat,,0,0,0,,我知道 虎姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:08.11,Cat,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:10.38,Cat,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:13.14,Cat,,0,0,0,,就現在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:18.53,Cat,,0,0,0,,就一下下…應該可以吧…
