Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,字典在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.58,0:23:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他們把字典藏起來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.42,0:23:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,藏哪了? 藏哪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,藏哪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:17.17,Cat,,0,0,0,,冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:20.01,Cat,,0,0,0,,飯在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,藏哪了!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:28.20,Cat,,0,0,0,,今天這麼熱鬧真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:29.96,Cat,,0,0,0,,根本不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:31.52,Cat,,0,0,0,,你不開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.52,0:23:33.76,Cat,,0,0,0,,我並非不是不開心!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:34.82,Cat,,0,0,0,,到底怎麼樣
